Mary Mara https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary_Mara 0 Mary Mara (born September 21, 1960) is an American TV and film actress from Syracuse, New York known for her recurring role as Inspector Bryn Carson on Nash Bridges and primetime dramas ER and Law Order. She also appeared in Mr. Saturday Night.
